    <a href="#32-%e5%85%b3%e9%94%ae%e6%8a%80%e6%9c%af%e7%bb%86%e8%8a%82" class="header-mark"></a>3.2 关键技术细节</h3><h4 id="321-空间并行交互机制spim" class="headerLink">
